{"tid":1745143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[區選文宣終極整合]想deadline fight最後2日做文宣既入黎","createTime":"2019-11-22T05:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T14:26:29.000Z","uid":51142,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0a38c1bd33227eb8fe5559faa44591a418f47097","tid":1745143,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"由於出面太多區選既文宣Post，所以整個集中Post懶人包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 點解區議會選舉咁重要？</strong></ins><br />\n我都唔多講喇 唔明既就自己睇啦 如果連你自己身處個區既議會都唔重要？咁幾時先重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【選戰必知】簡介區議會，點解區議會咁重要？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1255207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1255207</a><br />\n- 投邊個好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己識揀啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=337537e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2. 點解要文宣？</strong></ins><br />\n個個係連登度圍爐　打飛機　資訊停留係溫層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣要多D人知道啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍵盤戰又好 貼牆又好 貼屋企Lift口又好<br />\n比每個人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />登記左做選民要投票啊<br />\n最後羸定輸都好 最少要盡左力先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非定勇武都可以做<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3.文宣貼咩圖好？</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">常見問題：</span></strong><br />\n問：文宣貼唔貼得投咩黨？講下我個區投邊個侯選人，又唔好投邊個侯選人？<br />\n答：以上既都唔好做，最怕觸犯《選舉條例》，陣間DQ左d候選人(非建制)就唔好啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大方向係提返投票注意事項，區選既簡單資料，總之就係叫d人去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />詳細參考返文宣組既Post<br />\n[文宣組入] 唔好再好心做壞事: 唔好再整同貼同選舉有關既文宣!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/exinfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/exinfS</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>圖呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></ins><br />\n大量區選文宣 自行篩選(注意事項係上面提左)<br />\n文宣group tg link:(search #區選)<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=876c0d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己推介呢2張: <br />\n我覺得唔文宣圖唔洗多，少少地簡單，易明，睇到既人快get到就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prtQMeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FprtQMeT.jpg&h=57d9c3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJ1SUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJ1SUU.jpg&h=01a90bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4.有咩形式做文宣？</ins></strong><br />\n鏈盤：唔少得Facebook，IG，Air drop，whatsapp<br />\n痴牆：連儂牆、屋企Lift口(我大大力支持，原因：突破溫層文宣)<br />\n【行動post】《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5.文宣所需工具：</ins></strong><br />\n幾個人就可以組隊輕鬆快閃貼文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1油牆1貼紙1-2哨<br />\n每個人都可以輕鬆做文宣師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- <strong>高lv d</strong>就用牆紙粉開：<br />\n文宣組最新裝備：牆紙粉！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1578354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1578354</a><br />\n<br />\n- <strong>平民d</strong>就用麵粉粉開：<br />\n[區選] 和理非只需要$24.5就可以喺你自己住嗰座做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744407</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都想羸 我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一人出一分力 <br />\n比個目標自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最少貼自己住緊個座 係自己社區做好文宣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今星期日11月24號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家集中推整合post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />區選在即 deadline fight是必需的<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"959f9ed32fda777bcec7f123160d9579ede9294b","tid":1745143,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"開左個新整合Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"e28ddd077ae5b5b5daee822c6f71cef82c3eefef","tid":1745143,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"開左個新整合Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2/10"},{"pid":"36555d3b523c52c828d54d5dcab7ee68fc1f92a7","tid":1745143,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"開左個新整合Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"256ed3d4c5089e93015ca923cfa4e721fa6b84cb","tid":1745143,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"d93a2bc88f9e1fdb96cca8e1764c7f4fd69adfa1","tid":1745143,"uid":51142,"like":0,"